description: My target audience for this course is anyone who is ready to transform their life. They should take this course to motivate them and help them create the habits that are required to accomplish their goals. This course is about achieving personal transformation. Personal achievement would be the terminology my target audience would use to find my course. This course consists of module lectures. It will take about 30 minutes to complete this course. The course is structured into 5 sections, and within those 5 sections there will be lectures included. You should take this course if you want to achieve personal transformation.
title: How to achieve personal transformation.
